               <Entry_Name>Exposed Data</Entry_Name>
            </Taxonomy_Mapping>
         </Taxonomy_Mappings>
         <Mapping_Notes>
            <Usage>Allowed</Usage>
            <Rationale>This CWE entry is at the Variant level of abstraction, which is a preferred level of abstraction for mapping to the root causes of vulnerabilities.</Rationale>
